<h1><?php echo $header;?></h1>

<p>The recent changes page gives two options for viewing recent changes to the wiki: recently updated and recently created.</p>

<p>By default, Thresher will show users the 100 most recently updated items. Included in this list is the name of the page with a link to view the page, the person who made the udpate, when the update was made and any change comments they left when editing the page.</p>

<p>Clicking the Recently Created link at the top of the page will change the view to show the last 100 created items. Included in this list is the name of the page with a link to view the page, the person who created the page and the summary that was given of the page when it was created.</p>